Given this political fundraising email, respond with the name of the committee in the disclaimer that begins with Paid for by but does not include Paid for by, the committee address or the treasurer name. If no committee is present, return "None". Do not include any other text, no yapping.
name: Emily Randall (personal)
email: teamemily@electemilyrandall.com
subject: Real talk
body: Real talk, Peter — • We’re $2k short of our final end-of-month fundraisinggoal. • My Republican opponent says he has a poll showing him defeating me byone point. • Losing this Democratic seat could destroy our chances of takingback the House. This is the last fundraising deadline before the election.Election Day is in 5 days. We’re running a grassroots campaign with zeroCorporate PAC money, so I’m counting on a last-minute flood of donations fromsupporters like you. Please chip in what you can before the end-of-monthdeadline at midnight: er4c.com/midnight_deadline[https://er4c.com/midnight_deadline] I really appreciate anything you can give— and I’m proud to be in this fight together 💙 — Emily Paid for by EmilyRandall for Congress Emily Randall for Congress P.O.
